        "original_url": "https://duncancragg.substack.com/about",
        "fallback": "About - The Parallel Reality Computer",
        "text": "Future operating system research: app-free, Spatial and distributed approaches through pervasive, mashable, cross-host links. Click to read The Parallel Reality Computer, by Duncan Cragg, a Substack publication. Launched a year ago.",
